line_1: He paus'd a while, and kept his Maw,
He paus'd a while, and kept his Maw,
line_2: Till all their Lineaments he saw.

line_1: Hence birds of throat obscene, and greedy maw,
line_2: The chattering magpye, the tale-bearing daw,

line_1: And, blest with an accommodating maw,
line_2: Devour the luscious bit, red, recent, raw!

line_1: And next pale Av'rice with insatiate Maw;
line_2: Oppreffion nam'd — and stretch'd her filthy Claw,

line_1: All appetite had left his maw,
line_2: And age disarm'd his mumbling jaw.

line_1: Thousands too few to glut her rav'nous maw:
